short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides a list of percents calculations, in a simple way to understand you percentage calculation needs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides a list of percents calculations, but in a simple way to understand how it works and what kind of calculation you need in that moment!

This will help your productivity because you can do percentages calculations directly from you Google Chrome!
